  "abstract": "Soils of the Semi-Arid Tropics (SAT) are often low in organic matter. Concern about the maintenance of organic matter levels under conditions of intensified\r\nland-use makes knowledge of organic matter returns to soil by different crops and cropping systems important...... \r\n",
